f=\"https://youtu.be/s5SfYpMG4Gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs5SfYpMG4Gg&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRswHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=02cb15ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s5SfYpMG4Gg</a>"},{"pid":"b82034145b4140796b358ec54a2180e332f13f70","tid":402374,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"頭先貼錯link而家補貼<br />\n《出手》[Lyrics MV]<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=rr3MOoKlBGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drr3MOoKlBGw&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRswHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=756356b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=rr3MOoKlBGw</a>"},{"pid":"28d1fc6f7daeed754f756fb040771f4ef41a5226","tid":402374,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"估唔到無論喺邊度都好少人係陳凱彤粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6539e13cfabe95efa4311640d7ee989335f712a4","tid":402374,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170918/mobile/bkn-20170918035412231-0918_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170918%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170918035412231-0918_00862_001.html&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRswHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=503fcd46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170918/mobile/bkn-20170918035412231-0918_00862_001.html</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n英皇歌手陳凱彤（Lillian）日前與新加坡Youtuber黃維恒（Wilson）將《如果你也聽說》及《如果我變成回憶》兩首金曲串成一首歌翻唱，並認真地拍攝新MV，問到Lillian為何會與對方合作？她說：「經朋友介紹下識咗Wilson，之後佢話不如一齊玩吓啦，咁啱佢日前嚟咗香港，所以約埋一齊Jam咗首歌。」由於她在MV中從後攬住Wilson，問到會否感尷尬？Lillian說：「又冇喎，始終唔係面對面，冇眼部接觸。」隨即自爆有場對方伸手捲其秀髮時，Wilson尷尬得面紅紅，Lillian說：「因為佢要望住我，搞到企唔定，不過最後冇放入段片到，佢尷尬過我。」 <br />\n<br />\n寓工作於娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n對於Wilson為遷就她專程來港拍攝MV，問到對方是否對她有好感？Lillian說：「大家做嘢啫，我哋依家都仲有聯絡。（佢單身？）冇問佢。（有機會發展？）音樂上嘅發展，真係唔諗住喇，我事業心仲好重。」並大方透露對方來港寓工作於娛樂，Lillian說：「佢同屋企人嚟玩，順手拍埋MV。（有帶佢出去玩？）有呀。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">終於有新歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}